{"data":[{"date":"15:14 11/07","title":"\"Ch\u00f3 ti\u00ean tri\" d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/cho-tien-tri-du-doan-the-nao-ve-ket-qua-tran-croatia-vs-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede c\u1ea3 hai l\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0103n m\u00f3n th\u1ecbt b\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Anh, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Tam s\u01b0 th\u1eafng Croatia trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2>Psychic t\u1eebng \u0111o\u00e1n sai kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 n\u00e0y \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang 100% k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nay.<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1147","checkdouble":"190951"},{"date":"15:41 11/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 PSG chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Kante?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, PSG thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thiago Motta \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1982 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m NGolo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea-172-188620.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG quan t\u00e2m Kante</span> c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Sun c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Kante b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n n\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng minh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a PSG s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante duoc cham diem cao nhat tran Leicester vs Chelsea\" title=\"Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Leicester vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real,-Barca-va-PSG-muon-dua-tien-ve-Kante-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho Kante\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u00e0nh cho Kante, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kante l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues gi\u1eef Kante \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1146","checkdouble":"190952"},{"date":"16:03 11/07","title":"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa \u0110T Anh vs Croatia n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c k\u00ec l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Zlatko Dalic, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-1-4-1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marcelo Brozovic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, Brozovic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1n gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Croatia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf Croatia n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/4-viec-Croatia-can-lam-de-danh-bai-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Croatia n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 tr\u00ean Brozovic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric, Rebic, Perisic Rakitic c\u00f2n Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Mateo Kovacic c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Brozovic. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. HLV Southgate l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Dele Alli v\u00e0 Jesse Lingaard. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00ean khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Jordan Henderson, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 ch\u1edd th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<h2>3. Khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Kieran Trippier. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u1ea7n khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic c\u00f3 xu hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 Anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Mandzukic v\u00e0 Rebic c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Rebic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trippier\" title=\"Trippier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-16-nam-mot-tinh-yeu-nguyen-ven.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Croatia c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng Trippier</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng 'b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y' v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Croatia c\u1ea7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 Colombia l\u1eabn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire, Harry Kane v\u00e0 John Stones. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh hay chuy\u1ec1n b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a Young hay Trippier, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay &ndash; B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Anh vs Croatia v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u1eefng b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nCroatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Filip Tapalovic c\u0169ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1145","checkdouble":"190953"},{"date":"15:53 11/07","title":"\u201cSi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/bong-dung-mat-thuong-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Davor Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Suker ca ng\u1ee3i Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. T\u1edbi World Cup 2018, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang theo phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh t\u1ea1i Moscow, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia, Davor Suker \u2013 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/bong-dung-mat-thuong-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n 10 n\u0103m th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi. \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3\u201d, Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u00ean ESPN.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cModric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Croatia. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 phi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ea7u cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u01a1 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea3i Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Suker v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" title=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Mandzukic-phat-bieu-ve-Modric,-dong-doi-tai-DT-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i b\u1edfi t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ranh gi\u1edbi mong manh gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 50 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o 16 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf b\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 xem World Cup tr\u00ean TV.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t thi\u00eang li\u00eang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd x\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea7ng 2 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-nhan-tin-vui-truoc-tran-dai-chien-croatia-421-190921.html\">\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric-471-190912.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Croatia - T\u1eeb Davor Suker \u0111\u1ebfn Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\">Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1144","checkdouble":"190955"},{"date":"16:32 11/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khen ng\u1ee3i Pickford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/campos-phat-bieu-ve-pickford-thu-mon-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorge Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Campos c\u0169ng t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford b\u1ecb Courtois ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJordan Pickford \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft Colombia r\u1ed3i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Pickford nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/campos-phat-bieu-ve-pickford-thu-mon-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Pickford t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 1m85 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Campos b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorge Campos l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Pickford \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua. Anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi 130 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Mexico, c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf 2 k\u1ef3 World Cup 1994 v\u00e0 1998. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi Campos b\u1edfi chi\u1ec1u cao ch\u1ec9 1m70, r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p trong l\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Jorge Campos\" title=\"thu mon Jorge Campos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/thu-mon-Jorge-Campos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i. \u201c\u0110ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Jordan Pickford\u201d, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mexico n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 pha c\u1ee9u thua hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Brazil, n\u01a1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Hugo Lloris c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-10-bi-ty-so-rat-nho-cach-biet-rat-lon-421-190914.html\">Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-10-bi-mot-thoi-thuong-cua-bong-da-the-gioi-la-day-421-190903.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: M\u1ed1t th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1143","checkdouble":"190958"},{"date":"16:45 11/07","title":"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-viec-croatia-can-lam-de-danh-bai-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa \u0110T Anh vs Croatia n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c k\u00ec l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Zlatko Dalic, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-1-4-1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marcelo Brozovic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, Brozovic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1n gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Croatia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf Croatia n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/4-viec-Croatia-can-lam-de-danh-bai-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Croatia n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 tr\u00ean Brozovic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric, Rebic, Perisic Rakitic c\u00f2n Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Mateo Kovacic c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Brozovic. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. HLV Southgate l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Dele Alli v\u00e0 Jesse Lingaard. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00ean khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Jordan Henderson, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 ch\u1edd th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<h2>3. Khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Kieran Trippier. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u1ea7n khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic c\u00f3 xu hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 Anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Mandzukic v\u00e0 Rebic c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Rebic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trippier\" title=\"Trippier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-16-nam-mot-tinh-yeu-nguyen-ven.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Croatia c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng Trippier</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng 'b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y' v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Croatia c\u1ea7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 Colombia l\u1eabn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire, Harry Kane v\u00e0 John Stones. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh hay chuy\u1ec1n b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a Young hay Trippier, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay &ndash; B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Anh vs Croatia v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u1eefng b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nCroatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Filip Tapalovic c\u0169ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1142","checkdouble":"190960"},{"date":"16:59 11/07","title":"Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y, huy hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Santiago Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real Madrid n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Madrid n\u00f3i chung qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Infographics Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/Infographics-Cristiano-Ronaldo-chia-tay-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eed t\u1ebf v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00edn n\u0103m di\u1ec7u k\u1ef3 t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00edn n\u0103m th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Ch\u00edn n\u0103m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00ec nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5p. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo2\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163634-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo3\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163644-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay chia s\u1ebb ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m n\u1ed3ng \u1ea5m t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ba ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c b\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n trong n\u0103m n\u0103m. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1n Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ba danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i th\u1eadt qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo4\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo5\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163701-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea th\u1eddi gian ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo6\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo6\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163712-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo7\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163722-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Khu v\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m tr\u1ecdn trong tim t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i. H\u01a1n l\u00fac n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi: xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai tr\u01a1n tru \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo8\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163734-8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo9\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163744-9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo10\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163753-10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo11\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo11\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i, ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i hay b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo12\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo12\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo13\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo13\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Qua ch\u00edn n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1. T\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y, huy hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Santiago Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u n\u00f3i m\u00e0 ch\u00edn n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng h\u00e9t l\u00ean: Hala Madrid!&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Cristiano Ronaldo- <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em><strong>(D\u1ecbch: Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng GP)<br>\r\nInfographics by Marca (Vi\u1ec7t h\u00f3a b\u1edfi Bongda24h.vn)</strong></em></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1141","checkdouble":"190961"},{"date":"17:15 11/07","title":"Lucas Torreira \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/lucas-torreira-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-tien-ve-phong-ngu-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria, Lucas Torreira c\u00f3 31 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 0.88 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Lucas-Torreira-toi-Arsenal-Nang-cap-chat-thep-noi-tuyen-giua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira (s\u1ed1 14) c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Kante (26, 0.78 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Henderson (20, 0.83 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Matic (56, 1.62 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Fernandinho (65, 2.03 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Eric Dier (82, 2.61 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Arsenal th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 72 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 2.03 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. V\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Henderson (31, 1.28 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Fernandinho (47, 1.47 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Dier (48, 1.53 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Matic (64, 1.85 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m duy nh\u1ea5t Kante (85, 2.55&nbsp;l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eb7n b\u00f3ng, Torreira th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 57 l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi trung b\u00ecnh 1.61 l\u1ea7n, h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Henderson ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 40, Fernandinho l\u00e0 41, Dier v\u00e0 Kante c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 43 c\u00f2n Matic l\u00e0 56.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:</strong> Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Torreira l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal</span> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Torreira th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trung b\u00ecnh 61.83 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 87%. V\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n/90 ph\u00fat, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Kante (65), Dier (65), Matic (75), Henderson (86) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (93).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira tao ra kha nhieu cho cac dong doi\" title=\"Torreira t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/chuyen.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, con s\u1ed1 87% c\u1ee7a Torreira t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Henderson (84%) v\u00e0 Dier (86%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Matic (88%), Kante (89%) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (90%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 t\u1ea1o ra 36 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 1.02 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Dier (15), Fernandinho (21), Matic (24) v\u00e0 Henderson (25) nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Kante (41).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Torreira l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80%, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Henderson (53%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Kante, Matic (c\u00f9ng 83%), Dier (87%) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (88%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn: </strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Torreira kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, song s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 anh t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Torreira c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 2.85 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 68%. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Matic (59%), Fernandinho (60%), Henderson (60%), Kante (66%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Eric Dier (70%).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira co loi choi rat ran\" title=\"Torreira c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t r\u1eafn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/ran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t r\u1eafn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 k\u00e9m, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 39%, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n duy nh\u1ea5t Kante (35%) v\u00e0 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Fernandinho (55%), Dier (57%), Matic (67%) v\u00e0 Henderson (72%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m dai d\u1eb3ng, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trung b\u00ecnh anh ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 2.35 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Fernandinho (0.84), Matic (0.65), Henderson (0.58), Kante (0.45) v\u00e0 Dier (0.25).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:</strong> Torreira r\u1ea5t ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1140","checkdouble":"190962"},{"date":"17:46 11/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU s\u0103n sao s\u00e1ng Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/thuc-hu-vu-mu-san-rebic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic cho bi\u1ebft Eintract Frankfurt ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho Ante Rebic nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.</h2><h2>Rebic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Eintract Frankfurt theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Fiorentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Rebic \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Croatia v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Argentina 3-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 Rebic ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u1edf Premier League ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Man United, Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i Rebic. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<h2>Rebic ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thuc-hu-vu-mu-san-rebic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic c\u00f2n 3 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Frankfurt nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ante Rebic c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi th\u1ea5y Rebic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn cho Rebic. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 Rebic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Eintract Frankfurt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1139","checkdouble":"190963"},{"date":"17:40 11/07","title":"Anh vs Croatia: Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/anh-vs-croatia-con-moi-ngon-nhat-cho-bay-su-tu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea5y, ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng mong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi gi\u1edd. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u1ecd tr\u00ean hai kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh: ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u201cl\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\u201d th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 Colombia, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u2013 B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecf neo n\u00e0o n\u00edu gi\u1eef hy v\u1ecdng cho c\u1eb7p El Clasico?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, v\u1edbi linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u201cEl Clasico\u201d Luka Modric v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic, hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng khu v\u1ef1c b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">X\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng mang tr\u00ean b\u1eafp tay, Modric l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Croatia. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 10 hay s\u1ed1 8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ea5p s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 4 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean Rakitic l\u00e0m c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Anh-vs-Croatia-Con-moi-ngon-nhat-cho-bay-su-tu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zlatko Dalic tin t\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u1eafng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, v\u1edbi Mario Mandzukic h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi Andrej Kramaric tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, trong m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 nh\u01b0ng tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb gi\u1ed1ng 4-2-4 h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ante Rebic v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i khi Croatia c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao pressing ngay b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khi Nga ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u00f9ng Mandzukic v\u00e0 Kramaric h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 t\u1ea5u n\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn n\u00e0y, Mandzukic v\u00e0 Kramaric c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Croatia kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-thang-tien-o-world-cup-2018-hai-thap-ky-doi-cho-mot-the-he-vang-421-189353.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-thang-tien-o-world-cup-2018-hai-thap-ky-doi-cho-mot-the-he-vang-421-189353.html\">Croatia th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u1edf World Cup 2018: Hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nZlatko Dalic d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Argentina vs Croatia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng. H\u00f3a ra HLV 52 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh hoang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean n\u1eb1m n\u01a1i Modric, m\u1eabu nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 sau khi Kevin De Bruyne th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng B\u1ec9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Moskva \u0111\u00eam nay, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n, t\u1eeb ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m, \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n to cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh 1m73 c\u1ee7a anh, \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 ng\u1eafn d\u00e0i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean vai Dele Alli, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eef qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Anh-vs-Croatia-Con-moi-ngon-nhat-cho-bay-su-tu-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai c\u00fa s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Croatia, Rakitic c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng hay n\u00f3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. L\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi ng\u00f4i sao Barcelona ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Modric \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng knock-out tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1edbi gi\u1edd khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/argentina-va-con-ac-mong-nuoc-nga-messi-oan-minh-ganh-team-oan-minh-chiu-toi-den-bao-gio-421-189352.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Argentina ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span> \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i nh\u00f4 cao h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 sau l\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Casemiro hay Sergio Busquets \u1edf Real c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Barca. Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a n\u1eb1m \u1edf Marcelo Brozovic.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Croatia t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n cho Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e2y h\u00e3m, khai th\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Jordan Henderson. \u0110a d\u1ea1ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tay Dalic \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, kh\u00f4ng Brozovic th\u00ec Milan Badelj c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m \u201cm\u1ecf neo\u201d, hay khi c\u1ea7n phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Anh vs Croatia Con m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Anh-vs-Croatia-Con-moi-ngon-nhat-cho-bay-su-tu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i ngon nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea7y s\u01b0 t\u1eed?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Croatia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t sinh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sau 240 ph\u00fat qu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3o trong v\u00f2ng n\u0103m ng\u00e0y chinh chi\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Lovren v\u00e0 Vida \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Anh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Sterling v\u00e0 Lingard, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Harry Kane chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Lovren v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng Wembley th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i khi Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea1i 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham, v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Croatia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u201c\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d thay ra s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 sau n\u1eeda gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u01a1i b\u1edbt kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf kinh ho\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs Croatia ban ket World Cup 2018\" title=\"Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/172113-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea5y, ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng mong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t ch\u1ec9 h\u00ean xui \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 8/11 b\u00e0n t\u1edbi gi\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Tam S\u01b0 khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ham h\u1ed1 d\u00e2ng cao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan. Gareth Southgate ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 cho m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu-421-190786.html\">Raheem Sterling: Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1138","checkdouble":"190964"},{"date":"11:11 11/07","title":"Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/phap-10-bi-ty-so-rat-nho-cach-biet-rat-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275893/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-brazil-bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-tai-vong-ban-ket-421-190571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thomas Meunier d\u00ednh \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</span>. HLV Martinez v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Nacer Chadli tr\u00e1m c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Moussa Dembele b\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil, khi B\u1ec9 &ldquo;d\u1ee5&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ra \u0111\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Meunier khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <strong>H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng tung \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn &ldquo;c\u00f2 c\u01b0a&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00f9ng.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Du-am-tran-dau-Phap-vs-Bi-Ty-so-rat-nho,-cach-biet-rat-lon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tung \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 v\u1eady, c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f2n hay h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Romelu Lukaku, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n kevin De Bruyne c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c quen thu\u1ed9c, tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9. Trong 2 wingback, Chadli th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong. B\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Dembele ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c Marouane Fellaini ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, <strong>Ph\u00e1p&hellip; l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 ph\u00e1</strong>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng cho B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 chao \u0111\u1ea3o m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n<strong> &ldquo;si\u00eau xe&rdquo; </strong>Kylian Mbappe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Phap vs Bi Dembele te ca trong phong ngu tan cong Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/du-am-phap-10-bi-mot-thoi-thuong-cua-bong-da-the-gioi-la-day.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9: Mbappe li\u00ean t\u1ee5c cho Dembele h\u00edt kh\u00f3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mbappe sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec th\u00f3i ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span>. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c gi\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Mbappe ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng &ldquo;b\u00e0y tr\u00f2&rdquo;, khi chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a anh trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olivier Giroud b\u1ecb ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00ec li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi th\u00f3i &ldquo;ch\u00e2n g\u1ed7&rdquo;. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Giroud ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee9ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7, <strong>c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c lo.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng im ti\u1ebfng, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9, trong khi Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf &ldquo;th\u00f3i quen&rdquo; ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n, d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois. <strong>Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 hay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Giroud bo lo mot so co hoi cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Giroud-bo-lo-mot-so-co-hoi-cua-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud c\u00f3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 2 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u00e1t v\u00e1ch nhau, B\u1ec9 lu\u00f4n coi Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh trong m\u1ecdi l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c. D\u00e2n s\u1ed1 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n 6 l\u1ea7n (12 tri\u1ec7u vs 70 tri\u1ec7u), \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin. C\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1ec3 thao l\u00e0&hellip; <strong>Eddie Merckx</strong>, m\u1ed9t tay \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 73.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 coi Zidane l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 1. Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1eddi m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 s\u1eafm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n trong BHL &ndash; ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Henry, \u0111ang ng\u00e0y ng\u00e0y d\u1ea1y d\u1ed7 Romelu Lukaku &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Ph\u00e1p, khi 9/11 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0o nho\u00e1ng Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap g\u00ec cho B\u1ec9, khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean m\u00ecnh trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/boi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng 1 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1986, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Les Bleus h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf socola 2 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft EURO v\u00e0 World Cup, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ndash; so v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, B\u1ec9 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc hi\u1ec7n nay, nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m trong t\u00fai Raphael Varane, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n b\u1edfi &ldquo;c\u1eadu b\u00e9&rdquo; 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil ra &ldquo;d\u1ecda&rdquo; G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois, v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 &ldquo;tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u00e1t sao&rdquo; kia, m\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u00e2u trong \u0111\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p. \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n bung s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Thong-so-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1137","checkdouble":"190914"},{"date":"09:21 11/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">\u00a0<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Umtiti \u0103n m\u1eebng sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00fang v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho NHM m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u00e0n l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti. Trong pha l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 5 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtouis ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus n\u00f3i: \u201c\u0110\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i m\u1edbi xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n, tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y ra. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Umtiti t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh. \u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 k\u00edn k\u1ebd trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d, trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft sau 12 n\u0103m tuy nhi\u00ean Umtiti c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n\u00a0\u2018tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Paul Pogba sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1136","checkdouble":"190915"},{"date":"10:13 11/07","title":"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/vi-sao-mbappe-van-duoc-da-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-du-phai-nhan-2-the-vang-lien-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do cho chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup khi nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00ec sao Mbappe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft World Cup khi nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Vi-sao-Mbappe-van-duoc-da-chung-ket-World-Cup-khi-nhan-2-the-vang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Mbappe nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ch\u1ecbu thua k\u00e9m c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tinh ranh khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Uruguay, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha c\u00e2u gi\u1edd l\u1ed9 li\u1ec5u khi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n pha n\u00e9m bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90+3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u song Mbappe v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo lu\u1eadt m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a FIFA, c\u00e1c th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u0169 s\u1ebd\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00f3a khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Les Bleus \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190915.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p?</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan-421-190899.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan-421-190899.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9, Pogba gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1135","checkdouble":"190920"},{"date":"10:02 11/07","title":"\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/dt-anh-nhan-tin-vui-truoc-tran-dai-chien-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin vui khi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Henderson v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Luzhniki v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khi hai ng\u00f4i sao Henderson v\u00e0 Vardy l\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ngay sau khi \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay xu\u1ed1ng Moscow t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh Repino. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 g\u00e2n kheo trong khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Henderson DT Anh\" title=\"tien ve Henderson DT Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/sao-liverpool-bi-phe-truat-ngoi-thu-quan-anh-ngay-truoc-them-chung-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Tam S\u01b0 b\u1edfi Henderson \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, trong khi Jamie Vardy v\u1eabn l\u00e0 &lsquo;qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng&rsquo; v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9 l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Southgate s\u1ebd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t nh\u01b0 khi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua. S\u1edf d\u0129, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 do \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HLV Southgate, \u0110T anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3-5-2. Tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford. Kyle Walker, John Stones, Harry Maguire s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. 5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed3m Kieran Trippier, Jordan Henderson, Jesse Lingard, Dele Alli, Ashley Young. Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Sterling \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i khi m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Southgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea5y ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 k\u00e9o d\u00e3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h00 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai 12/7. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay &ndash; B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190881.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pickford-la-chia-khoa-giup-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190881.html\">&ldquo;Pickford l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nFabio Capello ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\">Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span><br>\r\nFilip Tapalovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, c\u1ef1u sao Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tam s\u01b0 nh\u1edd b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luka Modric v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1134","checkdouble":"190921"},{"date":"10:48 11/07","title":"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/kevi-de-bruyne-cay-cu-vi-cach-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p khi cho r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u00f4m h\u1eadn. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup (1986 v\u00e0 2018), \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai k\u1ef3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u thua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p*.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kevin De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/kevi-de-bruyne-cay-cu-vi-cach-thang-cua-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kevi De Bruyne cay c\u00fa v\u00ec c\u00e1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc 'b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd'? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c \u0110T Ph\u00e1p<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, Kevin De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n m\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Bruyne cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c cao v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i thua trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>* N\u0103m 1986, B\u1ec9 thua Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap-421-190916.html\">Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tien-ve-pogba-chia-se-chien-thang-truoc-bi-cung-doi-bong-nhi-vua-duoc-giai-cuu-188-190908.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba chia s\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\">Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1133","checkdouble":"190922"}]}